the hole is a 2001 psychological horror film directed by nick hamm , based on the novel after the hole by guy burt .   the film stars thora birch , whose headlining credit and highly publicized seven figure salary was attributed to her appearance in american beauty .   it also features keira knightley , in her first significant role in a feature film .   the film premiered in the united kingdom in april 2001 .   dimension films , which in october 2001 acquired the rights to distribute the film theatrically in the united states , never did so ; it was instead released direct-to-video nearly two years later , by dimension 's then-fellow disney subsidiary buena vista distribution .   the film was shot at bray studios and various locations around southern england , including downside school in somerset .